title: The Total Package! Balcony, dishwasher, full amenities!
posting_body: ['Call Apartment Guys at 773-549-3474 and ask for Reference #128732.', 'Large Gold Coast Rehabbed One Bedroom with a Balcony!', 'Amazing views from your floor to ceiling windows and private balcony!', 'Ideal location right on the Gold Coast and River North border!', ' this unit also has great closet space, central air conditioning, and newer kitchen with a dishwasher.', 'Located in a full amenity high-rise building with a sundeck, fitness center, business center, on-site grocery store, dry cleaners, and a salon!', 'Walking distance to great Gold Coast restaurants, shopping, entertainment, and much more!', 'Small cats and dogs are okay.', 'Prices are subject to change.***Photos may be of a similar unit.***For faster response best to call or text 773-549-3474 with reference #128732']
